[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/weak_twos"]
[Student "S"]
{EAST's hand has the look of a Weak Two-bid, but it is one point too strong. So she opens 1\S.

WEST naturally bids 2\C and EAST rebids the \S suit.

WEST always knew there would be a game bid, so with an 8-card fit he bids 4\S}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "S"]
[Vulnerable "None"]
[Deal "S:65.AQJ8753.975.5 AK9.94.AT86.9632 QJ83.T6.KJ4.KQJ4 T742.K2.Q32.AT87"]
