[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/weak_twos"]
[Student "S"]
{SOUTH is unsure whether to bid game or not. So she temporizes with 2NT.

NORTH shows an above average hand plus a high card in \Hs. 

SOUTH is no longer unsure, so she bids 4\S.}

